HEADWORD: Disencumbrance
<hw>Dis`en*cum"brance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Freedom or
deliverance from encumbrance, or anything burdensome or
troublesome.</def> <rj><au>Spectator.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
